high_descs: Turn around and then turn right to face the marble table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle in front of the glass.
Turn left and head to the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink to the right of the potato.
Pick up a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn right, go half way across the room and turn right to face the marble table.
Put the slice of potato in the pot to the right of the bread.
Pick up the pot with the slice of potato in it.
Turn left and head to the fridge.
Put the pot in the fridge on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot containing a slice of potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Go to the kitchen island
Pick up the farther knife with the yellow handle
Go to the sink
Cut the potato in the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Take a potato slice
Go to the kitchen island
Put the potato in a pot
Pick up the pot
Go to the fridge
Put the pot in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a potato slice in the fridge

high_descs: Turn left, move to the end of the island, near the knife.
Pick up the knife, near the bottle, from the island.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn right, move to the island in front of the pot.
Put the potato slice in the pot.
Pick up the pot from the island.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the pot in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of potato into a pot, place the pot into the refrigerator.
